Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好興奮呢，龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為再過不久\N就會見到龍媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.89,0:00:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.10,0:00:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣的高興\N我可愛的龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大老遠跑來的好辛苦\N媽媽在這裡唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍媽媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，我可愛的龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了慶祝重逢\N我們兩個到天空去散步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是擔心龍寶寶\N所以特別趕來迎接嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好美的母愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.89,0:00:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是媽媽唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好笑，沒想到還會上當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是暗妖精!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在騙人了，卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.43,0:01:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…只要沒有那隻龍寶寶在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就不算什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牠休息回來前\N我就可以先下手為強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.86,0:01:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你們再前進一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.23,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.73,0:01:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!\N餅乾我拿走了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.93,0:01:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經這麼多艱難\N我終於可以回黑暗之島…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.73,0:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為暴殄天物的關係嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.31,0:01:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那就是大龍山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.77,0:01:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回能見到真正的龍媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N我也終於能成為騎士了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.28,0:01:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!\N這麼一來我就回不去島上了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
